name: ***BREAKING NEWS*** A composition of the unconfirmed first images of 'The Thing'
description:
***BREAKING NEWS*** ***BREAKING NEWS*** ***BREAKING NEWS*** ***BREAKING NEWS*** ***BREAKING NEWS***

In a composition of yet to be confirmed first images of the birth of 'The Thing', these astounding images, it is believed, represent the initial chapter of life of 'The Thing' in gestation. There currently exists no knowledge of the next stages and ultimate birth of 'The Thing' and nor is it known how these images came to exist, who took them, and what happened to them in what would be very soon after these images were loaded into the metaverse.

However, it is now known there are no traces of existence of the capturer at all other than an extremely faint echo within spacetime that travels through other spaces and beyond, after which there is no echo at all.

It is assumed that this composition can be joined alongside objkt/461377 which is believed to be the "The Origin Space of ‘The Thing’".


A Dark Art Event
